description:
This is the additional puzzle pack for "Jigsaw Masterpieces 2". The following 10 puzzle images are included.
-Himeji Castle, Hyogo Prefecture
-Chidorigafuchi, Tokyo
-View of Mt. Fuji from Fujinomiya, Shizuoka Prefecture
-Three-storied Pagoda of Kiyomizu Temple, Kyoto
-Sakura Tsutsumi Park in Yoshimi-cho, Saitama Prefecture
-Cherry blossoms in full bloom in Kyoto
-Hirosaki Park, Aomori Prefecture
-Chureito Pagoda and Mt. Fuji, Shizuoka Prefecture
-Woman in kimono at a shrine in Kyoto
-View of Mt. Fuji from the Uruigawa River, Shizuoka Prefecture
name: Cherry Blossom Journey
